00:57:21,160 --> 00:57:23,190
I mean, how did you become a vegetarian?

782
00:57:24,020 --> 00:57:25,240
Because your mother was a vegetarian,

783
00:57:26,190 --> 00:57:27,230
what else?

784
00:57:29,090 --> 00:57:31,040
From where did you learn vegetarianism?

785
00:57:31,120 --> 00:57:32,160
Supposing you were a Muslim,

786
00:57:32,240 --> 00:57:36,070
then you would have eaten somebody's heads also!

787
00:57:40,200 --> 00:57:44,190
So luckily you are born in a Hindu community,

788
00:57:45,020 --> 00:57:47,120
but we go too far with it.

789
00:57:48,010 --> 00:57:49,240
Morning till evening -

790
00:57:50,080 --> 00:57:54,000
I mean, this ritualism is so much in Madras also

791
00:57:54,080 --> 00:57:55,080
that they told Me,

792
00:57:55,140 --> 00:57:58,060
"Mother, Sahaja Yoga can never work in Madras."

793
00:57:58,140 --> 00:58:00,000
I said, "Why?"

794
00:58:00,090 --> 00:58:02,170
"Because people are not at all sahaj.

795
00:58:03,010 --> 00:58:05,010
In the morning they must get up at four o'clock,

796
00:58:05,070 --> 00:58:08,110
have their bath, go to the temple, come back.

797
00:58:08,210 --> 00:58:10,070
If one day they don't do it,

798
00:58:10,160 --> 00:58:13,130
then the whole day they are like mad people,

799
00:58:15,100 --> 00:58:17,130
thinking they have committed the greatest sin -

800
00:58:17,200 --> 00:58:19,170
this routine must be done."

801
00:58:20,030 --> 00:58:22,030
There is no routine in Sahaja Yoga.

802
00:58:22,130 --> 00:58:24,100
It's a living process.

803
00:58:25,130 --> 00:58:28,130
There is no routine in living process.

804
00:58:29,080 --> 00:58:32,030
Whenever the flower wants, it will flower.

805
00:58:34,060 --> 00:58:37,170
So why kill yourself with these rituals?

806
00:58:38,080 --> 00:58:40,190
This is our problem in the Hindu religion,

807
00:58:41,010 --> 00:58:42,060
the same with the Christians;

808
00:58:42,140 --> 00:58:44,220
I mean, everybody is competing.

809
00:58:47,040 --> 00:58:50,070
God has created this world for us to enjoy.

810
00:58:51,240 --> 00:58:52,200
I tell you,

811
00:58:53,010 --> 00:58:56,160
if you give up this you'll be very much absolutely relaxed.

812
00:58:57,040 --> 00:58:58,160
Forget it!

813
00:59:00,120 --> 00:59:02,130
At the most, five minutes in the morning

814
00:59:02,240 --> 00:59:04,020
Sahaja Yoga meditation,

815
00:59:04,080 --> 00:59:07,030
and ten minutes in the evening before sleeping - finished.

816
00:59:07,110 --> 00:59:08,190
For that we have a center,

817
00:59:09,030 --> 00:59:11,160
you go and see them - that's all.

818
00:59:13,060 --> 00:59:15,170
The rest God will do for you.

819
00:59:20,040 --> 00:59:21,130
Now this is a nice question also -

820
00:59:21,200 --> 00:59:23,210
What is the final realization in sadhana?

821
00:59:24,050 --> 00:59:26,040
How should one proceed in that direction,

822
00:59:26,120 --> 00:59:29,190
after he feels the vibrations in his head and palms,

823
00:59:30,070 --> 00:59:31,140
initially? That's good,

824
00:59:31,200 --> 00:59:33,100
that means you have felt it, Mr. Subramaniam,

825
00:59:33,170 --> 00:59:35,040
and I'm happy to know about this.

826
00:59:35,040 --> 00:59:38,240
But I would say that you have to come to our center

827
00:59:39,070 --> 00:59:40,130
and proceed with it.

828
00:59:40,190 --> 00:59:43,100
But we don't talk of the future,

829
00:59:44,190 --> 00:59:46,180
we talk of the present.

830
00:59:47,230 --> 00:59:51,040
Slowly you will be surprised how you are rising,

831
00:59:53,010 --> 00:59:57,120
how you are really getting all the powers in yourself.

832
00:59:57,180 --> 01:00:00,180
You yourself will realize, and you will be amazed.

833
01:00:01,020 --> 01:00:02,100
I mean, you'll be surprised,

834
01:00:02,190 --> 01:00:05,110
some people I have met after one year -

835
01:00:05,210 --> 01:00:06,220
I have a very good memory,

836
01:00:07,030 --> 01:00:09,140
but I could not recognize them.

837
01:00:23,070 --> 01:00:25,090
Now, this gentleman is here,

838
01:00:26,000 --> 01:00:28,130
and he's something personal problem,

839
01:00:29,030 --> 01:00:30,020
poor thing.

840
01:00:30,100 --> 01:00:33,090
He went to this Navoli of Hatha Yoga,

841
01:00:33,210 --> 01:00:35,160
and he's suffering.

842
01:00:36,070 --> 01:00:39,220
This Hatha Yoga is another funny stuff.

843
01:00:41,020 --> 01:00:42,160
If you read Patanjali,

844
01:00:42,240 --> 01:00:44,140
you'll know it's Ashtanga Yoga.

845
01:00:45,140 --> 01:00:48,100
Out of this exercises, wee, wee, wee, wee,

846
01:00:48,170 --> 01:00:52,000
wee bit of that is so important.

847
01:00:52,110 --> 01:00:54,190
Anybody can come and teach you Hatha Yoga;

848
01:00:55,000 --> 01:00:56,190
unless and until he's a realized soul,

849
01:00:57,010 --> 01:00:59,140
he has no right to teach you anything.

850
01:01:00,230 --> 01:01:03,210
What I've said today is nirvichar samadhi,

851
01:01:04,120 --> 01:01:06,070
nirvikalpa - all is written there,

852
01:01:06,150 --> 01:01:09,020
and he calls all this all-pervading Power

853
01:01:09,100 --> 01:01:11,090
as ritambara pragya.

854
01:01:11,220 --> 01:01:17,130
Somebody teaches you something - "Ha, tha" - finished.

855
01:01:18,170 --> 01:01:22,060
People are running like mad, jumping like mad.

856
01:01:22,140 --> 01:01:24,220
You become right-sided, then you get heart attacks;

857
01:01:25,060 --> 01:01:26,190
now this gentleman has a problem.

858
01:01:27,040 --> 01:01:29,030
But I assure you, you'll be all right.

859
01:01:29,090 --> 01:01:31,030
You take to Sahaja Yoga, it's very simple,

860
01:01:31,090 --> 01:01:33,100
it will give you a balance, you'll be all right.

861
01:01:36,050 --> 01:01:39,140
Then Hatha Yoga, then going Gayatri Mantra:

862
01:01:39,230 --> 01:01:41,110
you become more right-sided.

863
01:01:41,190 --> 01:01:44,060
Learn what is needed for you.

864
01:01:44,140 --> 01:01:46,030
For a person who is right-sided,

865
01:01:46,120 --> 01:01:48,070
you have to have bhakti.

866
01:01:48,200 --> 01:01:52,100
Those who are left-sided have to have this.

867
01:01:53,140 --> 01:01:55,180
You have to give balance to yourself.

868
01:01:56,040 --> 01:02:00,070
And it will really give you such a joy.

869
01:02:01,050 --> 01:02:03,190
Otherwise if there's some Hatha yogi,

870
01:02:04,050 --> 01:02:06,030
you'd better approach him with a barge-pole;

871
01:02:06,110 --> 01:02:09,060
God knows when he will slap you - like Duruwasha

872
01:02:10,080 --> 01:02:11,200
It's very dangerous people.

873
01:02:13,030 --> 01:02:15,010
They don't know what is love is,

874
01:02:17,050 --> 01:02:20,070
they don't know what is Mother is.

875
01:02:20,170 --> 01:02:22,230
There's no talk of love.

876
01:02:33,000 --> 01:02:35,080
Is self-awareness

877
01:02:36,060 --> 01:02:42,030
a pre-requisite to practice on progress of

878
01:02:42,110 --> 01:02:46,140
realizing kundalini shakti? No.

879
01:02:48,040 --> 01:02:50,120
After realization you become self-aware.

880
01:02:50,210 --> 01:02:53,040
Nothing is needed.

881
01:02:55,040 --> 01:02:57,130
Now for example, people go on telling,

882
01:02:57,200 --> 01:02:59,160
"You have committed this sin. All right,

883
01:03:00,010 --> 01:03:04,130
pay so much money to me and all your sins will be finished."

884
01:03:05,040 --> 01:03:07,110
I tell you, put him to the police.

885
01:03:11,130 --> 01:03:15,030
To Me nobody is a sinner, no. You are My children.

886
01:03:16,150 --> 01:03:17,210
Nobody is a sinner.

887
01:03:17,240 --> 01:03:20,230
You have committed no sins, no wrong, nothing.

888
01:03:21,040 --> 01:03:23,150
You were mistaking something,

889
01:03:24,020 --> 01:03:27,000
you went into darkness;

890
01:03:27,110 --> 01:03:33,140
or I can say that you were ignorant, at the most.

891
01:03:34,120 --> 01:03:37,230
But I don't like to call any human being as a sinner,

892
01:03:38,060 --> 01:03:39,070
except for they're rakshasas.

893
01:03:39,160 --> 01:03:40,230
Of course there are rakshasas,

894
01:03:41,070 --> 01:03:42,130
then they are already branded,

895
01:03:42,210 --> 01:03:46,130
you don't have to say it, they're already there.

896
01:03:47,020 --> 01:03:52,140
So this self-awareness is what you have to get.

897
01:03:53,050 --> 01:03:55,030
We are not self-aware.

898
01:03:56,020 --> 01:03:58,160
By doing it, we cannot.

899
01:03:59,080 --> 01:04:00,230
When we say, "I have to be self-aware.

900
01:04:01,050 --> 01:04:03,060
Now I have to be self-aware, I have to go inside" -

901
01:04:03,160 --> 01:04:06,050
what are we using? Our ego.

902
01:04:09,150 --> 01:04:11,140
It's a happening.

903
01:04:12,060 --> 01:04:14,090
When you will achieve that state,

904
01:04:14,170 --> 01:04:17,090
that state - not human state,

905
01:04:17,200 --> 01:04:19,230
but a state of a yogi -

906
01:04:20,150 --> 01:04:25,150
there at that state you have self-awareness,

907
01:04:26,190 --> 01:04:28,210
and you respect yourself.

908
01:04:29,210 --> 01:04:31,240
You have your self-esteem.

909
01:04:33,020 --> 01:04:34,060
But you don't show off,

910
01:04:34,130 --> 01:04:36,110
you don't become cheapish person.

911
01:05:10,030 --> 01:05:11,000
He says that "Mother,

912
01:05:11,080 --> 01:05:15,070
I have recently started meditating in the Sahaja way,

913
01:05:15,140 --> 01:05:20,200
and I feel absolutely fresh and beautiful all the time.

914
01:05:21,030 --> 01:05:22,240
Though, Mother, put very humbly,

915
01:05:23,090 --> 01:05:25,230
say that the energy is our own,

916
01:05:26,050 --> 01:05:29,090
I have never felt this energy before.

917
01:05:29,190 --> 01:05:33,230
Mother, so kindly let us know if we are

918
01:05:35,200 --> 01:05:38,120
re-linked to the God or the main source,

919
01:05:38,200 --> 01:05:43,020
and that is the reason why we feel full of energy

920
01:05:43,100 --> 01:05:44,160
throughout?"

921
01:05:44,240 --> 01:05:47,020
Of course, you are feeling because you are re-linked,

922
01:05:47,080 --> 01:05:48,130
no doubt about it.

923
01:05:49,080 --> 01:05:52,230
But you don't feel any energy because

924
01:05:53,170 --> 01:05:56,000
you must be a very good man.

925
01:05:57,070 --> 01:05:59,040
When there is obstruction,

926
01:05:59,140 --> 01:06:03,120
then only you feel a little problem.

927
01:06:04,030 --> 01:06:05,230
Like a smooth landing,

928
01:06:06,070 --> 01:06:07,060
you don't feel it;

929
01:06:07,120 --> 01:06:09,120
if you get a smooth landing in Sahaja Yoga,

930
01:06:09,180 --> 01:06:13,040
means you are a very nice person,

931
01:06:13,190 --> 01:06:16,020
very good man, righteous man.

932
01:06:16,110 --> 01:06:20,100
Just smoothly you land, there's no obstruction, nothing.

933
01:06:20,170 --> 01:06:22,020
You have no imbalances,

934
01:06:22,100 --> 01:06:24,130
you are in the center, no problem.

935
01:06:25,030 --> 01:06:27,060
But if you have problems,

936
01:06:27,160 --> 01:06:32,090
then the kundalini a little bit goes, comes down.

937
01:06:35,150 --> 01:06:37,140
And that's why you don't feel it.

938
01:06:37,240 --> 01:06:39,040
Those who have problems

939
01:06:39,100 --> 01:06:42,180
do feel a little pain sometimes here and there.

940
01:06:43,220 --> 01:06:46,030
But if the kundalini just rises up,

941
01:06:46,140 --> 01:06:50,100
know that you are righteous, you are good.

942
01:07:01,040 --> 01:07:04,230
Is the term "God" given to all unexplainable questions

943
01:07:05,070 --> 01:07:07,070
as their explanation manas? No, no, no.

944
01:07:07,160 --> 01:07:09,210
In Sahaja Yoga everything is explained

945
01:07:10,050 --> 01:07:13,020
and can be proved Pramana.

946
01:07:21,020 --> 01:07:24,110
Has anyone seen, heard, felt or realized

947
01:07:24,190 --> 01:07:29,010
his ultimate control, master, owner, decision-maker?

948
01:07:29,070 --> 01:07:33,230
Of course! So many of them, don't you know?

949
01:07:36,100 --> 01:07:38,100
There are so many.

950
01:07:45,240 --> 01:07:49,160
Does the final authority lives outside every man,

951
01:07:49,240 --> 01:07:52,160
or does it reside inside everyone?

952
01:07:52,220 --> 01:07:55,030
He is reflected in everyone,

953
01:07:57,060 --> 01:08:03,060
but the reflection cannot be the object.

954
01:08:04,160 --> 01:08:07,160
But the reflection can be equal to the object,

955
01:08:07,220 --> 01:08:10,030
depending on the reflector.

956
01:08:16,070 --> 01:08:21,130
If anyone has realized the ultimate truth, why did he die?

957
01:08:40,210 --> 01:08:43,020
These are big, big things he has asked.

958
01:08:43,090 --> 01:08:44,210
You see, I think the gentleman 

959
01:08:45,020 --> 01:08:46,150
who is asking Me this question,

960
01:08:46,210 --> 01:08:49,080
I would ask him first of all to get your realization.

961
01:08:49,160 --> 01:08:51,190
He's quite confused gentleman.

962
01:08:53,160 --> 01:08:58,130
You see, just now - "What is God? What is death?"

963
01:08:59,160 --> 01:09:01,070
What are you?

964
01:09:01,160 --> 01:09:03,160
Find out first.

965
01:09:04,060 --> 01:09:06,170
Who is asking this question? ....

966
01:09:10,110 --> 01:09:14,050
He is asking from a center? Oh, my God!

967
01:09:15,220 --> 01:09:17,040
It's interesting, eh,

968
01:09:17,120 --> 01:09:19,200
that he's asking from a center all these questions.

969
01:09:20,040 --> 01:09:23,100
That means he's too much thinking, thinking, thinking.

970
01:09:37,010 --> 01:09:39,230
Is wrong to say that God is in good?

971
01:09:40,070 --> 01:09:42,200
I think he's done too much reading,

972
01:09:44,100 --> 01:09:45,190
that's the problem.

973
01:09:46,040 --> 01:09:48,160
First you know the reality, My child,

974
01:09:49,070 --> 01:09:54,020
then all these questions will disappear - nirvikalpa. ....

975
01:10:08,220 --> 01:10:13,100
Now he's talking about ideal good and all that.

976
01:10:20,240 --> 01:10:24,010
It's definitely true that man lives only once ...

977
01:10:24,070 --> 01:10:28,100
It's wrong. Who told you that? He doesn't.

978
01:10:31,130 --> 01:10:33,140
But if you believe in that I cannot help it,

979
01:10:33,210 --> 01:10:35,140
but it's not so.

980
01:10:36,020 --> 01:10:39,130
And that to be good and to be righteous

981
01:10:39,200 --> 01:10:43,010
is not the end of your search.

982
01:10:45,220 --> 01:10:49,060
Dharma is the balance,

983
01:10:50,180 --> 01:10:52,070
that gives you the balance.

984
01:10:52,150 --> 01:10:55,030
But balance for what, dharma for what?

985
01:10:55,100 --> 01:10:56,210
We should ask the question.

986
01:10:57,040 --> 01:11:00,240
Why should we be dharmic; why not be adharmic?

987
01:11:01,070 --> 01:11:04,220
Why not ask such a question? It's logical.

988
01:11:05,070 --> 01:11:09,020
Why do all this dharma, dharma, dharma?

989
01:11:10,080 --> 01:11:13,020
Because you have to rise.

990
01:11:13,110 --> 01:11:16,030
Say an aeroplane is not balanced,

991
01:11:16,130 --> 01:11:17,160
how will it rise?

992
01:11:18,000 --> 01:11:21,090
But supposing it is only balanced and never rises,

993
01:11:21,170 --> 01:11:24,090
what's the use of making an aeroplane?

994
01:11:25,110 --> 01:11:27,150
So you have to be dharmateet.

995
01:11:28,010 --> 01:11:30,010
You have to go beyond dharma,

996
01:11:30,120 --> 01:11:33,200
you have to go beyond gunas - it's gunateet -

997
01:11:34,040 --> 01:11:38,150
you cross over, then dharma becomes part and parcel of you.

998
01:11:39,140 --> 01:11:42,120
You don't have to tell yourself, "Don't do this, don't ..."

999
01:11:42,200 --> 01:11:45,220
No, you just don't do it, try anything.

1000
01:11:49,110 --> 01:11:50,210
I'll tell you My own example.

1001
01:11:51,060 --> 01:11:53,010
You know I have a double life.

1002
01:11:53,120 --> 01:11:57,180
My husband is a - what is he, you must have known about him

1003
01:11:58,030 --> 01:12:00,230
- he's a big, big, big boss of something,

1004
01:12:02,170 --> 01:12:07,070
and I've lived with all that nonsense all My life.

1005
01:12:09,170 --> 01:12:12,030
When he went to England

1006
01:12:13,190 --> 01:12:16,180
they asked him, "Why don't you have dancing with us?"

1007
01:12:17,010 --> 01:12:18,170
He said, "Because my wife doesn't dance,

1008
01:12:19,000 --> 01:12:20,150
I don't want to dance." He puts everything on Me,

1009
01:12:20,230 --> 01:12:23,090
it's a very good way of escaping!

1010
01:12:24,030 --> 01:12:26,120
So they said, "No, no, bring Her to London,

1011
01:12:26,200 --> 01:12:27,200
She'll be all right.

1012
01:12:28,010 --> 01:12:29,130
If you bring Her to London She'll start dancing."

1013
01:12:29,210 --> 01:12:32,080
He said, "You even take Her to moon, She will not!"

1014
01:12:33,090 --> 01:12:38,170
So this is what it is. The dharma is innate, you just don't do it.

1015
01:12:39,040 --> 01:12:43,140
Not because of conditioning, or it's better - it is Sahaj.

1016
01:12:45,050 --> 01:12:48,030
Sahaja, you - just, you just don't do it.

1017
01:12:48,130 --> 01:12:50,170
"No, I will not do that."

1018
01:12:52,010 --> 01:12:54,030
You will never do wrong things,

1019
01:12:54,100 --> 01:12:58,100
because you will just not do it.

1020
01:13:02,070 --> 01:13:04,070
So this has to go beyond dharma,

1021
01:13:04,130 --> 01:13:06,080
means the dharma is part and parcel of that.

1022
01:13:06,160 --> 01:13:11,050
Gunateet means you are beyond gunas.

1023
01:13:14,020 --> 01:13:16,100
You are neither right-sided, left-sided, centered,

1024
01:13:16,190 --> 01:13:18,000
but you are beyond.

1025
01:13:18,080 --> 01:13:20,190
What is left, right, center, what is this,

1026
01:13:21,020 --> 01:13:24,020
why to hang like that? - better be above.

1027
01:13:25,060 --> 01:13:27,030
That is what happens to you.

1028
01:13:27,100 --> 01:13:29,050
So "only there are righteous people":

1029
01:13:29,130 --> 01:13:31,160
many righteous people came and went away,

1030
01:13:31,220 --> 01:13:34,050
had no effect on the public.

1031
01:13:34,180 --> 01:13:40,190
What is needed is your emancipation, your ascent;

1032
01:13:41,050 --> 01:13:43,080
that's what we have to achieve.

1033
01:13:45,220 --> 01:13:48,030
"Only the good" - so-called good;

1034
01:13:48,140 --> 01:13:51,150
and you cannot establish good, I tell you.

1035
01:13:52,190 --> 01:13:55,150
Nobody likes to follow a good person.

1036
01:13:58,140 --> 01:14:01,100
Like in Pune they were saying,

1037
01:14:01,170 --> 01:14:05,100
"Everybody takes - they eats money, they never eat food."

1038
01:14:05,180 --> 01:14:07,210
I said, "Really?"

1039
01:14:08,040 --> 01:14:09,070
So I told My husband,

1040
01:14:09,140 --> 01:14:11,070
"Everybody eats money" - he was in London.

1041
01:14:11,160 --> 01:14:14,190
He said, "You tell them My husband never took any bribe.'"

1042
01:14:15,020 --> 01:14:17,030
So I told them, "My husband never took any bribe."

1043
01:14:17,110 --> 01:14:19,220
They said, "Why didn't he take? Who told him not to take?"

1044
01:14:23,030 --> 01:14:26,190
So what happens is

1045
01:14:27,070 --> 01:14:31,080
that normally people never follow a person who is

1046
01:14:31,160 --> 01:14:34,020
good and righteous, never.

1047
01:14:36,030 --> 01:14:38,220
But they'll always follow a person who is a

1048
01:14:39,050 --> 01:14:40,030
little bit like this.

1049
01:14:40,110 --> 01:14:44,070
The reason is, we are coming from animal stage -

1050
01:14:45,010 --> 01:14:47,070
easy to go back.

1051
01:14:49,050 --> 01:14:54,190
But once you're realized, then it's difficult;

1052
01:14:56,010 --> 01:14:58,110
means once the flower becomes the fruit,

1053
01:14:58,200 --> 01:15:03,220
it cannot become the flower - as simple as that.

1054
01:15:04,070 --> 01:15:09,100
So I say you've come here, all right, very sweetly,

1055
01:15:10,030 --> 01:15:14,060
and then get your realization; then I'll talk to you.

1056
01:15:14,210 --> 01:15:16,230
Then you yourself will say - and now,

1057
01:15:17,050 --> 01:15:18,120
see these people who were singing here,

1058
01:15:18,210 --> 01:15:22,070
some of them were terrible drug addicts, terrible!

1059
01:15:22,230 --> 01:15:24,020
They couldn't even see Me. They said,

1060
01:15:24,080 --> 01:15:26,010
"We saw these lights coming out of You,

1061
01:15:26,080 --> 01:15:29,220
never saw You" when they came - in comas.

1062
01:15:30,150 --> 01:15:34,180
Overnight, finished - alcoholics, overnight.

1063
01:15:35,010 --> 01:15:36,180
I didn't tell them. I never tell,

1064
01:15:37,030 --> 01:15:39,100
"Don't drink, don't ..." I never use that word.

1065
01:15:39,230 --> 01:15:43,180
Let the light of your spirit come in, and you are there.

1066
01:15:45,210 --> 01:15:47,100
I don't have to tell you anything,

1067
01:15:47,180 --> 01:15:50,080
all habits you'll drop by yourself.

1068
01:15:54,100 --> 01:15:56,020
Do you see the point?

1069
01:15:57,060 --> 01:15:59,130
Because when the light comes in,

1070
01:16:01,030 --> 01:16:03,050
the darkness has to run away.

1071
01:16:05,230 --> 01:16:08,010
So righteousness is not sufficient enough.

1072
01:16:08,080 --> 01:16:10,150
You have to go beyond that.

1073
01:16:30,160 --> 01:16:35,050
Somebody has written about his friend who has a problem,

1074
01:16:35,130 --> 01:16:37,170
who's fallen down, had an accident.

1075
01:16:38,000 --> 01:16:42,190
He should go and ask the Sahaja yogis to help him.

1076
01:16:43,030 --> 01:16:46,040
Nowadays I don't cure people, because there's no need to;

1077
01:16:46,150 --> 01:16:49,040
I'm doing all other nonsensical things.

1078
01:16:49,180 --> 01:16:53,010
The curing nowadays' done by Sahaja yogis.

1079
01:16:55,170 --> 01:16:58,010
There are so many other things I have to see to.

1080
01:16:58,150 --> 01:16:59,200
So you call anyone,

1081
01:17:00,020 --> 01:17:03,010
they'll be very helpful and they will do it.

1082
01:17:07,170 --> 01:17:10,050
Ah, it's a good question -

1083
01:17:12,190 --> 01:17:15,180
Is it possible to cure the suffering and poor

1084
01:17:16,000 --> 01:17:17,100
with this Sahaja Yoga?

1085
01:17:17,170 --> 01:17:19,220
Can we get rid of our poverty?

1086
01:17:20,080 --> 01:17:24,110
We can, by all means -

1087
01:17:26,200 --> 01:17:30,010
if you stop fasting first.

1088
01:17:30,230 --> 01:17:34,050
You want to fast? "All right," God says, "all right, go ahead. 

1089
01:17:34,130 --> 01:17:38,110
You'll not get food." Finished! Your wish will be fulfilled.

1090
01:17:39,180 --> 01:17:41,220
You want to become like a sanyasi?

1091
01:17:42,190 --> 01:17:45,240
Want to wear torn clothes? All right, have poverty.

1092
01:17:46,060 --> 01:17:49,060
You want poverty, after all you asked for it.

1093
01:17:55,190 --> 01:17:58,000
Then, you want sufferings? "We must suffer."

1094
01:17:58,090 --> 01:18:00,170
There's so many nonsensical things going on

1095
01:18:01,020 --> 01:18:03,080
that "you must suffer." Then how?

1096
01:18:03,140 --> 01:18:07,080
"I have suffer " - all right, if you want that, you enjoy it.

1097
01:18:10,040 --> 01:18:12,210
You ask for prosperity, you'll get it,

1098
01:18:13,210 --> 01:18:16,010
after kundalini awakening.

1099
01:18:16,070 --> 01:18:19,130
You see the center there, called as the Nabhi Chakra,

1100
01:18:19,230 --> 01:18:22,160
and who is sitting there is Lakshmi Narayana.

1101
01:18:23,120 --> 01:18:26,010
Once Lakshmi Narayana is awakened within you,

1102
01:18:26,160 --> 01:18:28,210
how can you be poor?

1103
01:18:32,180 --> 01:18:35,190
But also money has its own problems.

1104
01:18:37,190 --> 01:18:43,030
You get wealth, which is satisfying.

1105
01:18:45,170 --> 01:18:48,060
But don't ask for poverty.

1106
01:18:48,230 --> 01:18:53,040
Leave alone you, now the Westerners have got

1107
01:18:54,070 --> 01:18:56,180
a great desire for poverty.

1108
01:18:57,200 --> 01:18:59,210
They wear pants, they said they are holey,

1109
01:19:00,020 --> 01:19:01,180
means there are holes.

1110
01:19:02,100 --> 01:19:06,020
Torn pants they wear - in England, imagine,

1111
01:19:06,130 --> 01:19:09,070
such a cold country, wearing holey pants,

1112
01:19:09,240 --> 01:19:11,220
getting varicose veins.

1113
01:19:12,080 --> 01:19:16,080
And so many nonsensical suffering is going on there,

1114
01:19:16,160 --> 01:19:18,060
so many.

1115
01:19:18,140 --> 01:19:21,190
(Such a long letter - should write small one.)

1116
01:19:23,050 --> 01:19:29,170
So that's going on, and that's how people ask for it.

1117
01:19:30,010 --> 01:19:33,060
So there is recession in America, recession in England,

1118
01:19:33,140 --> 01:19:37,140
recession in Spain, crawling into France - have it.

1119
01:19:37,220 --> 01:19:40,070
If you want to have poverty, have it.

1120
01:19:41,130 --> 01:19:44,090
So the Lakshmi chit is going to come this side, I think.

1121
01:19:45,040 --> 01:19:47,020
Some sense is coming into our government,

1122
01:19:47,100 --> 01:19:53,080
and I'm sure it will work out - hope so.

1123
01:19:53,210 --> 01:19:56,080
But you take to Sahaja Yoga and you'll be surprised.

1124
01:19:56,210 --> 01:20:00,190
For example, in England we have such a lot of unemployment,

1125
01:20:01,020 --> 01:20:04,200
but not one Sahaja yogi is unemployed, not one.

1126
01:20:06,160 --> 01:20:11,150
At least with this fellow one at least ...

1127
01:20:12,000 --> 01:20:15,150
he will take to Sahaja Yoga, to begin with.

1128
01:20:21,200 --> 01:20:27,070
Mother, Sahaja Yoga is for health and joy

1129
01:20:27,150 --> 01:20:31,010
only, or is it something more? Everything - totality.

1130
01:20:31,110 --> 01:20:32,210
What do you want?

1131
01:20:33,210 --> 01:20:35,110
Ask for it,

1132
01:20:38,060 --> 01:20:42,000
desire for it - everything.

1133
01:20:56,210 --> 01:20:58,170
He says it's not explained to him.

1134
01:20:59,060 --> 01:21:00,230
You see, just now I'll give you realization,

1135
01:21:01,060 --> 01:21:03,200
you will see how the chakras are opened out and all that.

1136
01:21:04,020 --> 01:21:06,120
But later on if you go to the center you can know

1137
01:21:06,190 --> 01:21:10,100
everything, in one year you'll be all masters.

1138
01:21:11,130 --> 01:21:13,240
But give some time to yourself, is the point.

1139
01:21:14,070 --> 01:21:15,190
People are very busy these days.

1140
01:21:16,020 --> 01:21:17,060
What are you doing?

1141
01:21:17,160 --> 01:21:21,060
Some ladies told Me they're very busy with [*]kitty parties!

1142
01:21:25,200 --> 01:21:27,110
Here are very few ladies in here,

1143
01:21:27,190 --> 01:21:30,110
Madras; all the ladies must be in the temple sitting,

1144
01:21:31,010 --> 01:21:34,120
cutting, shaving their heads.

1145
01:21:39,030 --> 01:21:41,120
And very educated women also do it.

1146
01:21:41,240 --> 01:21:44,020
I mean, why, why should we shave your head?

1147
01:21:44,100 --> 01:21:47,070
God has lots of hair - you don't have to cut.

1148
01:21:49,110 --> 01:21:51,100
All this nonsense!

1149
01:21:55,180 --> 01:21:59,080
Women can be much more shakti shali than men,

1150
01:21:59,200 --> 01:22:04,080
but this conditioning of the women of India - God knows.

1151
01:22:06,100 --> 01:22:09,070
All right. So now we are ...

1152
01:22:17,040 --> 01:22:19,010
He's saying, "I have been practising pranayama

1153
01:22:19,090 --> 01:22:23,120
for four years. I don't have teacher ..." Very dangerous.

1154
01:22:26,020 --> 01:22:28,180
If you have no teacher, whether you have teacher or not,

1155
01:22:29,000 --> 01:22:31,220
pranayama is very dangerous.

1156
01:22:35,080 --> 01:22:40,060
Ha! If you have problem with your lungs,

1157
01:22:41,030 --> 01:22:43,060
or some specific reason ....

1158
01:22:43,160 --> 01:22:45,060
You see, all these vyayamas (means exercise),

1159
01:22:45,150 --> 01:22:49,070
were given for specific reason, for specific chakras.

1160
01:22:49,150 --> 01:22:50,220
Now, the kundalini's rising;

1161
01:22:51,040 --> 01:22:54,240
supposing she stops at your stomach, Nabhi,

1162
01:22:55,150 --> 01:22:58,130
and you are doing pranayama, what's the use?

1163
01:23:00,180 --> 01:23:02,190
You should know where the kundalini is there.

1164
01:23:03,010 --> 01:23:06,050
For example, today I was coming by car.

1165
01:23:08,050 --> 01:23:12,180
Now they stopped Me at one point, then at second point.

1166
01:23:13,020 --> 01:23:14,140
When the car started moving,

1167
01:23:14,210 --> 01:23:17,050
then only I knew where it is going to stop.

1168
01:23:17,200 --> 01:23:20,060
Beforehand, how can I do it?

1169
01:23:21,190 --> 01:23:22,170
In the same way,

1170
01:23:22,230 --> 01:23:25,050
when kundalini rises - use your brains! -

1171
01:23:25,150 --> 01:23:27,010
then she stops at a point,

1172
01:23:27,080 --> 01:23:33,010
then you should know by what vyayama you can put it right.

1173
01:23:33,150 --> 01:23:35,040
It's very scientific.

1174
01:23:35,150 --> 01:23:40,060
We too use, but not like all the medicines from

1175
01:23:40,180 --> 01:23:43,070
the medicine box taking,

1176
01:23:43,210 --> 01:23:45,120
morning till evening.

1177
01:23:45,240 --> 01:23:49,200
And that's why they say they develop problems - they do.

1178
01:24:03,000 --> 01:24:05,030
You will, very soon.

1179
01:24:07,000 --> 01:24:08,240
It's a very dangerous thing.

1180
01:24:11,110 --> 01:24:15,190
You see, actually we are not only physical being.

1181
01:24:16,010 --> 01:24:19,110
We don't live in only on prana - that's right.

1182
01:24:20,140 --> 01:24:23,070
I've seen people who practise pranayama,

1183
01:24:23,180 --> 01:24:25,120
if they're married - thank God you're not married -

1184
01:24:25,200 --> 01:24:27,180
they divorce their wives,

1185
01:24:28,030 --> 01:24:30,030
because there's no love.

1186
01:24:33,050 --> 01:24:36,170
They're very dry people, extremely dried up;

1187
01:24:38,200 --> 01:24:41,090
no poetry in their life.

1188
01:24:42,140 --> 01:24:46,010
All right, you'd better start reading some nice poetry!

1189
01:24:50,120 --> 01:24:51,120
Now, he is saying there -

1190
01:24:51,200 --> 01:24:54,210
"Could you please tell what is right-sided and left-sided?"

1191
01:24:55,100 --> 01:24:57,040
It's quite a long subject,

1192
01:24:57,110 --> 01:24:59,080
but if you go to Sahaja Yoga they will tell you.

1193
01:24:59,140 --> 01:25:06,190
Right-sided is physical and emotional energy,

1194
01:25:07,050 --> 01:25:13,030
used for physical and - sorry, physical and mental work.

1195
01:25:13,170 --> 01:25:17,030
Left-sided is the energy for emotions.

1196
01:25:17,110 --> 01:25:19,040
Now for example, he's doing pranayama.

1197
01:25:19,120 --> 01:25:22,000
He's doing that, he'll become right-sided -

1198
01:25:24,150 --> 01:25:26,210
only if you do that.

1199
01:25:37,070 --> 01:25:43,220
When the kundalini is in the process of awakening,

1200
01:25:44,130 --> 01:25:46,000
is one getting fear?

1201
01:25:46,000 --> 01:25:48,140
No, you do not. She's your mother.

1202
01:25:49,000 --> 01:25:50,190
She will bear all the problems.

1203
01:25:51,000 --> 01:25:53,220
When you were born, your mother bore all the problems,

1204
01:25:54,050 --> 01:25:56,220
all the labor pains. She didn't trouble you, did she?

1205
01:26:00,000 --> 01:26:02,120
She, poor thing, suffered for you.

1206
01:26:02,210 --> 01:26:04,230
And once you are born she forgets everything,

1207
01:26:05,060 --> 01:26:07,060
"That's - my child is born now, finished.

1208
01:26:07,160 --> 01:26:09,070
Whatever is over is over."

1209
01:26:09,150 --> 01:26:11,070
That's what is kundalini.

1210
01:26:11,240 --> 01:26:13,140
Why should you have any fear?

1211
01:26:13,230 --> 01:26:16,010
This is people who are telling you that

1212
01:26:16,130 --> 01:26:18,210
kundalini awakening is very dangerous and all that,

1213
01:26:19,040 --> 01:26:20,130
because they don't know anything about it.

1214
01:26:20,240 --> 01:26:23,120
They don't want you to get your realization.

1215
01:26:32,190 --> 01:26:34,100
What he says is true,

1216
01:26:34,200 --> 01:26:39,000
that - [Question:"Evil exists from time immemorial,

1217
01:26:39,090 --> 01:26:47,060
in spite of several incarnations and saints."]

1218
01:26:49,010 --> 01:26:50,180
It's correct;

1219
01:26:51,200 --> 01:26:53,180
but there is a solution.

1220
01:26:54,130 --> 01:26:57,240
So why not seek the solution, to get out of evil?

1221
01:26:58,180 --> 01:27:02,120
Once you are a realized soul,

1222
01:27:02,190 --> 01:27:05,130
the evil will run away - not you.

1223
01:27:12,100 --> 01:27:15,210
The time has come for all the evil to run away,

1224
01:27:16,120 --> 01:27:19,130
to be destroyed, to be exposed, to be finished.

1225
01:27:20,020 --> 01:27:22,150
It's you who can do it.

1226
01:27:25,100 --> 01:27:30,000
Everything takes its own time, like the growth of a tree.

1227
01:27:31,030 --> 01:27:35,170
Slowly, slowly all these six chakras were worked out.

1228
01:27:36,030 --> 01:27:39,020
Now the question of the seventh chakra, is the Sahasrara,

1229
01:27:39,150 --> 01:27:42,010
which is now worked out in Sahaja Yoga.

1230
01:27:44,100 --> 01:27:46,190
So the picture is complete.

1231
01:27:49,210 --> 01:27:56,020
Evil cannot destroy a Sahaja yogi; they know it very well.

1232
01:27:57,140 --> 01:28:00,170
Even the evil know that they cannot.

1233
01:28:02,010 --> 01:28:05,090
If they see a Sahaja yogi, they run away.

1234
01:28:09,230 --> 01:28:11,230
So don't you worry.

1235
01:28:18,090 --> 01:28:20,240
I think I have answered all your questions,

1236
01:28:21,100 --> 01:28:23,010
most of them;

1237
01:28:26,240 --> 01:28:28,160
but there's one thing.

1238
01:28:30,050 --> 01:28:34,060
I've been doing this for the last (how many years?) -

1239
01:28:38,000 --> 01:28:40,200
twenty-three years, twenty-one years,

1240
01:28:42,110 --> 01:28:44,090
answering questions.

1241
01:28:46,160 --> 01:28:49,010
I'm quite now clever,

1242
01:28:49,070 --> 01:28:52,170
I can answer any question, that's true.

1243
01:28:53,080 --> 01:28:56,200
But this is no guarantee for your awakening,

1244
01:28:57,030 --> 01:29:00,080
I must tell you. It's a mental acrobat.

1245
01:29:04,200 --> 01:29:06,160
So though I have answered your question,

1246
01:29:06,220 --> 01:29:09,060
doesn't mean that I will raise your kundalini,

1247
01:29:09,140 --> 01:29:11,090
or kundalini will rise.

1248
01:29:11,170 --> 01:29:14,000
That's a separate issue altogether.

1249
01:29:14,200 --> 01:29:18,200
But I don't want you to have this mind suddenly

1250
01:29:19,010 --> 01:29:22,130
shooting out and saying that you didn't ask this question,

1251
01:29:22,210 --> 01:29:25,010
so that you be stressed out. That's why I answer.

1252
01:29:25,130 --> 01:29:27,080
Otherwise makes no difference whether I answer

1253
01:29:27,140 --> 01:29:29,020
or don't answer.

1254
01:29:29,190 --> 01:29:31,170
It's something very different,

1255
01:29:32,190 --> 01:29:34,160
different area.

1256
01:29:44,200 --> 01:29:49,030
So now, we are all prepared for our realization.

1257
01:29:49,200 --> 01:29:54,120
Those who got yesterday also will get it more.

1258
01:29:56,020 --> 01:29:58,230
As I have told you, those who do not want to have it,

1259
01:29:59,060 --> 01:30:03,050
I cannot force on you - cannot force.

1260
01:30:12,170 --> 01:30:16,090
I think all the Sahaja yogis from the West have to go out -

1261
01:30:16,240 --> 01:30:19,230
this time is there, sorry.

1262
01:30:20,160 --> 01:30:23,040
I know you want to sit down for meditation,

1263
01:30:23,130 --> 01:30:26,020
but you'll be getting much more chances than others;

1264
01:30:26,110 --> 01:30:27,240
because there's time up.

1265
01:30:28,080 --> 01:30:30,070
You have to pack up your things.

1266
01:30:30,170 --> 01:30:32,060
All right.

1267
01:30:34,200 --> 01:30:36,200
Look at them, they're singing Sanskrit,

1268
01:30:37,080 --> 01:30:39,150
and it's complete "Ai Giri Nandini" they sing so well.

1269
01:30:39,230 --> 01:30:42,090
Just think of them - can you imagine, these people,

1270
01:30:43,080 --> 01:30:44,150
how did they learn?

1271
01:30:44,230 --> 01:30:47,060
These are Germans, can you imagine?

1272
01:30:47,230 --> 01:30:50,060
They don't call themselves Germans, no.

1273
01:30:50,210 --> 01:30:52,210
How could they do it?

1274
01:30:55,070 --> 01:30:57,180
They didn't know, these English didn't know a word

1275
01:30:57,240 --> 01:31:01,020
of Hindi; they lived here for three hundred years,

1276
01:31:01,100 --> 01:31:03,070
I don't know what they did.

1277
01:31:04,010 --> 01:31:06,110
Even to tell them Darwaza Band Kar (means close the door)

1278
01:31:06,180 --> 01:31:09,000
you had to say, "There was a banker."

1279
01:31:09,170 --> 01:31:11,130
Look at them!

1280
01:31:11,240 --> 01:31:14,050
All this is the Atma!

1281
01:31:15,020 --> 01:31:16,200
How they appreciate your music,

1282
01:31:17,020 --> 01:31:20,050
and how they appreciate your Kuchipudi dancing out,

1283
01:31:20,110 --> 01:31:22,200
it's surprising -

1284
01:31:24,050 --> 01:31:26,190
much more than you can.

1285
01:31:33,060 --> 01:31:40,070
Because our music comes from Aumkara.

1286
01:31:43,040 --> 01:31:45,090
It will be proved, Brahman.

1287
01:31:47,010 --> 01:31:49,190
