01:55:27,000 --> 01:55:31,170
"Mother, I am not guilty."

1546
01:55:32,000 --> 01:55:34,030
Say it sixteen times, please.

1547
01:55:34,140 --> 01:55:39,230
"Mother, I am nirdosh. I'm absolutely nirdosh."

1548
01:55:48,130 --> 01:55:50,120
I have already told you

1549
01:55:50,230 --> 01:55:52,150
that whether you forgive or don't forgive,

1550
01:55:52,210 --> 01:55:56,210
you don't do anything; it's a myth.

1551
01:55:58,180 --> 01:56:03,170
But when you don't forgive, then you play into wrong hands

1552
01:56:08,090 --> 01:56:12,000
and torture yourself, while the person who has tortured you

1553
01:56:12,090 --> 01:56:14,080
is quite happy.

1554
01:56:14,220 --> 01:56:20,150
So now, raise your right hand on your forehead across,

1555
01:56:20,240 --> 01:56:24,010
and put down your head.

1556
01:56:26,050 --> 01:56:29,140
Fully put down your head, and here

1557
01:56:33,150 --> 01:56:37,180
you have to say from your heart, not how many times.

1558
01:56:38,170 --> 01:56:40,060
If you don't say it,

1559
01:56:40,120 --> 01:56:45,180
I cannot make your kundalini pass through this constricted

1560
01:56:46,010 --> 01:56:47,120
Agnya Chakra.

1561
01:56:47,120 --> 01:56:49,210
So please, all of you should say,

1562
01:56:50,040 --> 01:56:55,050
"Mother, I forgive everyone in general,"

1563
01:56:55,170 --> 01:57:00,130
not thinking about anyone in particular, please.

1564
01:57:12,140 --> 01:57:17,150
Now, take back your hand on the back side of your head.

1565
01:57:21,210 --> 01:57:27,050
Push back your head, as far as possible.

1566
01:57:29,050 --> 01:57:31,180
Without feeling guilty,

1567
01:57:36,080 --> 01:57:38,190
without counting your mistakes,

1568
01:57:39,060 --> 01:57:43,230
just for your satisfaction you have to say,

1569
01:57:44,110 --> 01:57:46,110
"Oh divine Power,

1570
01:57:46,220 --> 01:57:50,120
please forgive me if I have done anything wrong.

1571
01:57:50,220 --> 01:57:57,070
Oh Brahmachaitanya, please forgive me if I have done

1572
01:57:57,150 --> 01:58:00,020
anything wrong, knowingly or unknowingly."

1573
01:58:00,210 --> 01:58:06,210
This you have to say in your heart,

1574
01:58:07,100 --> 01:58:09,240
not how many times.

1575
01:58:17,150 --> 01:58:19,160
Now,

1576
01:58:24,110 --> 01:58:28,080
stretch your right hand.

1577
01:58:30,110 --> 01:58:35,140
Put the center of your palm of right hand

1578
01:58:36,030 --> 01:58:39,150
on top of the fontanel bone area,

1579
01:58:40,000 --> 01:58:44,030
which was a soft bone in your childhood.

1580
01:58:45,120 --> 01:58:49,040
Push back your fingers as far as possible.

1581
01:58:50,070 --> 01:58:54,070
Put down your head as far as possible.

1582
01:58:56,050 --> 01:58:58,050
Here again,

1583
01:58:59,160 --> 01:59:04,130
I cannot force Self-realization on you,

1584
01:59:05,210 --> 01:59:08,030
so you have to ask for it.

1585
01:59:09,170 --> 01:59:13,220
Move your scalp seven times clockwise,

1586
01:59:14,140 --> 01:59:19,150
saying, "Mother, please give me my Self-realization."

1587
01:59:20,010 --> 01:59:22,070
Seven times, please.

1588
01:59:24,010 --> 01:59:26,140
Don't move the hand so much as the scalp.

1589
01:59:26,210 --> 01:59:28,230
Please press it hard. Push back your fingers.

1590
01:59:29,060 --> 01:59:30,210
First is, unless until you push back fingers,

1591
01:59:31,040 --> 01:59:33,070
there won't be any pressure.

1592
02:00:29,060 --> 02:00:31,220
Now take down your hands, please.

1593
02:00:35,050 --> 02:00:37,140
Put both the hands towards Me.

1594
02:00:39,170 --> 02:00:42,140
Now watch Me without thinking.

1595
02:00:50,130 --> 02:00:52,240
Now put your right hand towards Me,

1596
02:00:53,090 --> 02:00:55,240
and bend your head and see for yourself.

1597
02:00:56,050 --> 02:00:57,190
Don't watch others, watch yourself.

1598
02:00:58,040 --> 02:01:01,030
See if there's a cool breeze coming out of your

1599
02:01:01,130 --> 02:01:02,220
fontanel bone area,

1600
02:01:03,050 --> 02:01:06,160
see if there's a cool breeze coming out of your

1601
02:01:06,220 --> 02:01:08,080
fontanel bone area.

1602
02:01:08,160 --> 02:01:12,220
There might be a hot breeze also;

1603
02:01:13,080 --> 02:01:15,090
if you have not forgiven, specially,

1604
02:01:15,180 --> 02:01:17,180
then the hot breeze might be there.

1605
02:01:18,150 --> 02:01:21,000
So now you forgive.

1606
02:01:22,120 --> 02:01:26,200
Now, take your left hand towards Me like this.

1607
02:01:27,070 --> 02:01:29,070
Again put down your head.

1608
02:01:29,160 --> 02:01:31,240
Not on top, but away from it;

1609
02:01:32,070 --> 02:01:34,020
some people get it very far also.

1610
02:01:34,130 --> 02:01:37,110
Try to see if there's a cool breeze

1611
02:01:37,190 --> 02:01:41,100
or a hot breeze coming out of your head.

1612
02:01:42,080 --> 02:01:45,200
On the fontanel, not very far backward and forward,

1613
02:01:46,030 --> 02:01:49,120
but on the fontanel, on the taloo.

1614
02:01:54,140 --> 02:01:56,000
All right?

1615
02:01:56,110 --> 02:01:59,230
Again, put your right hand towards Me.

1616
02:02:00,130 --> 02:02:04,100
Ha! Bend your head, bend your head.

1617
02:02:07,180 --> 02:02:09,130
That's it!

1618
02:02:10,120 --> 02:02:12,040
Now,

1619
02:02:12,160 --> 02:02:16,070
I have to tell you how to give yourself the Kavach

1620
02:02:16,160 --> 02:02:17,220
to protect yourself,

1621
02:02:18,050 --> 02:02:19,190
it's very important;

1622
02:02:20,060 --> 02:02:22,030
and how to raise your kundalini,

1623
02:02:22,110 --> 02:02:25,230
it's very important, very simple - he'll show you also.

1624
02:02:26,190 --> 02:02:29,140
Put your left hand like this in front of you,

1625
02:02:30,050 --> 02:02:31,140
and the right hand you have to move,

1626
02:02:31,220 --> 02:02:33,190
the left hand goes straight.

1627
02:02:34,080 --> 02:02:37,000
So you have to - I'll just show you first of all, like this.

1628
02:02:37,080 --> 02:02:43,110
It goes up onto your head, and here you give it one knot.

1629
02:02:45,010 --> 02:02:47,110
Now, again we'll start now, properly.

1630
02:02:48,030 --> 02:02:50,030
We start it from here.

1631
02:02:50,090 --> 02:02:53,130
Now start moving your left hand upward.

1632
02:02:54,090 --> 02:02:56,230
For fixing up your kundalini,

1633
02:02:57,070 --> 02:03:00,230
put your hand up and give it one knot;

1634
02:03:02,190 --> 02:03:05,010
then again, the second one.

1635
02:03:09,140 --> 02:03:11,230
Give it the second knot.

1636
02:03:12,090 --> 02:03:14,100
Third knot you have to give three times.

1637
02:03:14,180 --> 02:03:16,240
Now again do it, please:

1638
02:03:22,100 --> 02:03:26,210
one, it's two,

1639
02:03:28,030 --> 02:03:32,210
and three. Done! Now the Kavach.

1640
02:03:33,080 --> 02:03:36,130
You have to take for your protection every morning

1641
02:03:36,210 --> 02:03:40,050
when you go out, and before sleeping you should

1642
02:03:40,110 --> 02:03:42,060
put your attention here and sleep off.

1643
02:03:42,160 --> 02:03:45,080
Put the left hand towards Me like this.

1644
02:03:49,010 --> 02:03:51,070
It is Saadhe teen...

1645
02:03:52,010 --> 02:03:55,230
the three-and-a half coils.

1646
02:03:56,200 --> 02:03:58,100
So how do you give Kavach?

1647
02:03:58,180 --> 02:04:02,010
It's, put left hand towards Me, towards the photograph,

1648
02:04:02,100 --> 02:04:04,120
put the right hand like this -

1649
02:04:04,220 --> 02:04:06,090
I'll show you first of all.

1650
02:04:06,170 --> 02:04:11,110
Then raise it like this, bring it down - this is half.

1651
02:04:12,170 --> 02:04:17,040
Then again you take it back - this is one.

1652
02:04:18,060 --> 02:04:25,040
Again you take it up, is again you take it back - is two.

1653
02:04:26,120 --> 02:04:30,020
Again you take it like this,

1654
02:04:31,190 --> 02:04:34,020
again you bring it back - is three.

1655
02:04:34,120 --> 02:04:36,100
And now you take it back only halfway,

1656
02:04:36,180 --> 02:04:39,010
so three-and-a-half times.

1657
02:04:42,110 --> 02:04:45,160
This is bandhan, is the Kavach,

1658
02:04:46,090 --> 02:04:49,010
Kavach of protection.

1659
02:04:51,000 --> 02:04:52,180
Also lots of things you'll learn,

1660
02:04:53,030 --> 02:04:55,120
how to use this power from your hand.

1661
02:04:55,190 --> 02:04:57,220
Now, all those who have felt

1662
02:04:58,200 --> 02:05:01,170
cool or hot breeze in their hands

1663
02:05:02,010 --> 02:05:05,040
or out of your fontanel bone area,

1664
02:05:06,070 --> 02:05:08,030
please raise your both hands.

1665
02:05:08,100 --> 02:05:12,010
All those who have felt, please raise both your hands.

1666
02:05:15,050 --> 02:05:17,210
They have a little problem of liver, but it will work out,

1667
02:05:18,040 --> 02:05:20,100
it doesn't matter.

1668
02:05:21,170 --> 02:05:23,090
May God bless you all,

1669
02:05:23,170 --> 02:05:25,200
may God bless you.

1670
02:05:32,120 --> 02:05:36,180
So Madras should become now Mada Raas,

1671
02:05:37,020 --> 02:05:39,180
means all the Mada (vanity) is finished

1672
02:05:42,110 --> 02:05:44,240
and achieve that state.

1673
02:05:45,160 --> 02:05:49,040
May God bless you all. Again and again I tell you,

1674
02:05:50,180 --> 02:05:54,070
be humble and come to the center.

1675
02:05:54,160 --> 02:05:57,190
There are some very good Sahaja yogis in the center.

1676
02:05:58,080 --> 02:06:02,110
They'll all tell you everything with very loving way.

1677
02:06:03,030 --> 02:06:07,190
But please come, and pay attention to yourself,

1678
02:06:09,120 --> 02:06:12,000
and know everything.

